{"tid":2227181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中秋夜祥華邨躁漢當街打老婆 普通話大嗌「我要她死」","createTime":"2020-10-02T14:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T17:38:09.000Z","uid":271829,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"d26ffe2967ca4b327e24c96f6b1ea343a2731bf6","tid":2227181,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T14:43:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/X06vJ8Vw4JOoly7Bn3HYMyz5Rd0=/496x256/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XH37FGXCVVB7HG2F7YMUWQIDDE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FX06vJ8Vw4JOoly7Bn3HYMyz5Rd0%3D%2F496x256%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXH37FGXCVVB7HG2F7YMUWQIDDE.jpg&h=bb910a5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n縱使白衫男被途人拉住，仍不斷揮拳毆打妻子。街坊提供<br />\n...<br />\n中秋理應人月兩團圓，但粉嶺祥華邨一名男子，竟在街頭揮拳毆打妻子，其間扯頭髮、勾拳及腳踢等招數盡出，又揚言要殺死對方。<br />\n事發於周五（2日）凌晨零時許。有街坊目擊情況，指一名穿白衫的男子懷疑醉酒，在粉嶺祥華邨的士站附近與妻子發生爭執，其後白衫男突然動手一直追打妻子，又趁妻子逃跑倒地之際，補上一腳，踢向對方胸口，之後更揮拳毆面及身體至少7下。附近途經的市民見狀，立即上前喝止，又高呼「喂！做咩打人呀」。<br />\n有熱心市民將白衫男試圖拉開，阻止他再毆打妻子，但白衫男繼續破口大罵，甚至出手扯妻子的頭髮長達近半分鐘，一直不肯放手。有市民不齒白衫男的行為，質問他「點解要打女人」，但白衫男竟爆粗指罵「我打老婆關你X事呀」，之後又用普通話表示「我要她死」。未幾白衫男突然倒地，而一直拉住他的市民亦連帶跌倒地上。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201002/KGMM7MP4DVDP7BY3XOAGKVBW6M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201002%2FKGMM7MP4DVDP7BY3XOAGKVBW6M%2F&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=3e5d7108\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201002%2FKGMM7MP4DVDP7BY3XOAGKVBW6M%2F&h=ed00f621\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201002/KGMM7MP4DVDP7BY3XOAGKVBW6M/</a>"},{"pid":"3561939f16d127e8a7b69d6e8cc1117711dff7bd","tid":2227181,"uid":228143,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T14:45:03.000Z","msg":"蝗打蝗又好似真係唔關其他人事<img src=